#Text=Does that make you feel uncomfortable ?
#Text=Are there some times where you are like , “ I do n’t want to punish the Jew . ”
#Text=It all depends on the person and how they are taking it .
#Text=During session you can tell whether it is going too far , or whether it is something that is very emotional for a person .
#Text=You both have to go into it understanding that it is a role play .
#Text=And a lot of times they ’ll tell me , “ Look , it ’s okay , you can call me this , this and that .
#Text=It ’s fine . ”
#Text=With experiences like that , do you experience personal growth and contend with your own hang-ups or why certain things bother you ?
#Text=It really does .
#Text=It ’s surprising how much you learn about yourself and another person .
#Text=A lot of things you learn from here — which for some people is surprising — you apply to your own life .
#Text=Can you given an example ?
#Text=Well , you learn to be more open-minded to people .
#Text=More understanding to a man ’s needs rather than , “ This is the way you ’re supposed to be .
#Text=This is the way society has made you .
#Text=You ca n’t be a sissy maid , you have to be the macho man all the time . ”
#Text=You know ?
#Text=It makes you understand that there are multiple sides to everybody rather than what you see is what you get .
#Text=I have worked here for a few months and I am still surprised by the people who come in .
#Text=[ Rebecca comes in and asks if we will leave The Blue Room for Alex ’s session and go to The Gold Room to continue the interview ]
#Text=Psychology II
#Text=Mistress Veronica in The Gold Room at Rebecca 's Hidden Chamber .
#Text=Is it important for you to know the motivations of the clients ?
#Text=It is something you need to be aware of and something you need to be able to tell during your session .
#Text=You feel it , you sense it , by speaking with someone and dealing with someone in that way , you are able to tell whether it is an actual problem that they have .
#Text=They are very open with us and they tell us a lot of things .
#Text=You are in constant discussion .
#Text=It ’s not just the physical aspect of S&M , where there ’s the whipping and spanking , it ’s also very verbal .
#Text=You are constantly talking to each other and there ’s a lot of times where you can tell whether it ’s just a regular fetish or whether it is an actual psychological problem these people have .
#Text=And there have been a few people like that .
#Text=Can you give an example ?
